Package quest

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Question
    This interface represents the methods for all question type objects.
    Questionnaire
    This interface represents the functions used to create an array of question objects that can be used in a question bank.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractQuestion
    This class contains abstract methods used by all of the question type objects.
    HashFormula
    This class represents a formula that will replace the hashCode.
    LikertQuestion
    This class creates Likert type questions.
    MultipleAnswerQuestion
    This class creates multiple choice questions.
    MultipleChoiceQuestion
    This class creates multiple choice questions.
    QuestionnaireArray
    Allows the creating of an array of question type objects to use in a question bank.
    QuestionnaireTest
    Class to test created questionnaire lists.
    QuestionTest  
    TextComparator<Question>
    This class allows for the sorting of two question objects by their question text in lexicographical order.
    TypeComparator<Question>
    This class allows for the sorting of two question objects by their type.
    YesNoQuestion
    This class allows creating yes/no questions.
